name: DumbMoney
description: The GameStop saga showcased community strength against traditional finance. Every degen who invested in the GME stock was dubbed an "APE" by the media and on television... and that's how the term "APE" gained fame in the crypto world. (https://www.dumbmoneytoken.vip/thestory) Drawing inspiration from this, some apes from reddit and GME decided to code $GME token on Ethereum , a symbol of united community apes against conventional markets. With the launch of the DumbMoney Movie, X (Twitter) will be swarmed by $GME. So, we, the smart apes, will explode in popularity and dominate every connection thanks to this and to our narrative.
